clive is a command line tool for extracting videos from Youtube,
Google Video, Dailymotion, Guba (free), Stage6, Metacafe, LastFm, 
Sevenload websites. clive is written in Python and is cross-platform.

Main features:

    - Video extraction
    - Integration and re-encoding with 'ffmpeg'
    - Player integration with a 3rd party software

WWW:	http://home.gna.org/clive/
